2011-03-19 # 2.0

[NEW] Redesigned Operation API.




2011-02-23 # 1.2

[NEW] The `wdp:files:attached` markup.

[CHG] Updated the attached files loading using the new ActiveRecord features.

[CHG] Rename AttachedFiles as Attachments.




2010-09-05 # 1.0

[NEW] The WdAttachedFilesElement class can be used to create elements to manage files attached to
nodes.

[NEW] The `attached_files` getter is adding to instances of the `system_nodes_WdActiveRecord` class
using the new features of the FObject class.

[NEW] Attached images are created using the "resources.files" module.

[DEL] Removed the FancyUpload code.

[FIX] Sometimes the temporary name generated by PHP for uploaded files is the same, resulting in
uploaded files overwriting each other.  